OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening with outbreaks, turning
OL,7,Fheavier for a time later. Becoming dry
OL,8,Ffor a time overnight, before further
OL,9,Fcloud and patchy rain arrive from the
OL,10,Fwest later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FCloudy and breezy throughout
OL,13,Fthe day as outbreaks of rain move
OL,14,Feast, these heavy at times. Some drier
OL,15,Fand brighter spells in the west later
OL,16,Fas the rain clears away.
OL,17,
OL,18,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FBright
OL,19,For sunny spells and scattered showers
OL,20,Ffrom Monday to Wednesday, heavy and
OL,21,Fthundery at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
